name: part_002
file: tmp_【 3DLIVE 】ねね～ちらい～ぶ４年目もよろしくね！ゲストいっぱいでお祝い！【 #桃鈴ねねの４年目 】 [5Ney9Z_WnTU]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_002.mov

scenes.description: Momosuzu Nene interacts with the audience and shoots signed balls while moving on a beetle-shaped platform.
Momosuzu Nene performs the song 'Hana no Tou'.

subtitles.original: ...ない 目いっぱい
subtitles.english: ...not, as hard as I can,

subtitles.original: 咲かせるよ
subtitles.english: I'll make it bloom.

subtitles.original: 自分という名の大きな花
subtitles.english: A great flower called myself,

subtitles.original: 満開のモモノネ
subtitles.english: the Momonone in full bloom.

subtitles.original: よいしょー！みんなー！
subtitles.english: Heave-ho! Everyone!

subtitles.original: おうちにプレゼントが届いてる人、
subtitles.english: If a present has arrived at your home,

subtitles.original: 開けてください！
subtitles.english: please open it!

subtitles.original: おりゃあー！
subtitles.english: Oryaa!

subtitles.original: 食らえ！ねねの...
subtitles.english: Take this! Nene's...

subtitles.original: 何が入ってるかと言うと...
subtitles.english: As for what's inside...

subtitles.original: ねねのサインボール砲だ！
subtitles.english: it's Nene's signed ball cannon!

subtitles.original: おら食らえ！
subtitles.english: Take that!

subtitles.original: おらおらおらおらおら！みんな、飛ぶぞー！
subtitles.english: Ora ora ora ora ora! Everyone, we're taking flight!

subtitles.original: うをぉぉぉー！おらおらおらおらおら！
subtitles.english: Uwoooo! Take that, take that, take that!

subtitles.original: すごい量が出るんだから！
subtitles.english: Because a huge amount is coming out!

subtitles.original: おら！下の人もおら！
subtitles.english: Hey! You people below too!

subtitles.original: 真下の人も食らえ！
subtitles.english: The people right underneath, take this too!

subtitles.original: 直下で！うをぉぉぉー！
subtitles.english: Direct hit! Uwoooo!

subtitles.original: 思いは太陽の光浴びて
subtitles.english: Thoughts bask in the sunlight,

subtitles.original: 鮮やかに輝くよ 空を全部
subtitles.english: and shine brightly, across the whole sky.

subtitles.original: おおーおーおーおー
subtitles.english: Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

subtitles.original: 目いっぱいこの両手広げてさ
subtitles.english: Spread these hands as wide as you can.

subtitles.original: ありがとみんな！開けてくれたかな？
subtitles.english: Thank you, everyone! Did you open it?

subtitles.original: ツイッターとかよかったら載せて見せてね！
subtitles.english: If you'd like, post it on Twitter and show me!

subtitles.original: おいえ！
subtitles.english: Oh yeah!

subtitles.original: はっ！
subtitles.english: Ha!

subtitles.original: あぶなーい！
subtitles.english: That was close!

subtitles.original: みんながいれば何でもできるよ
subtitles.english: With all of you, I can do anything.

subtitles.original: 思いのまま すぐの道
subtitles.english: A straight path as my heart desires.

subtitles.original: で行け あの空に届くように
subtitles.english: Go, so that you reach that sky.

subtitles.original: もう怖いものなんてない
subtitles.english: There's nothing to be afraid of anymore.

subtitles.original: 目いっぱい咲かせるよ みんなで咲かそう
subtitles.english: I'll make it bloom; let's all make it bloom together.

subtitles.original: たくさんの花
subtitles.english: So many flowers.

subtitles.original: 満開のモモノネ
subtitles.english: The Momonone in full bloom.

subtitles.original: みんな見て！なに？
subtitles.english: Everyone, look! What is it?

subtitles.original: ねねは何に一体乗ってるんだ？
subtitles.english: What on earth is Nene riding?

subtitles.original: これはなんだなんだー？
subtitles.english: What is this, what is this?

subtitles.original: うわ！あ！地面が！地面が来るー！
subtitles.english: Whoa! Ah! The ground! The ground is coming!

subtitles.original: 花の塔
subtitles.english: Flower Tower

subtitles.original: 作詞・作曲：さユり 編曲：名越由貴也 (MUSIC FOR MUSIC)
subtitles.english: Lyrics/Composition: Sayuri / Arrangement: Yukiya Nagoshi (MUSIC FOR MUSIC)

subtitles.original: 君が持ってきた漫画
subtitles.english: The manga you brought,

subtitles.original: くれた知らない名前の花
subtitles.english: the flowers you gave me with names I didn't know.

subtitles.original: 今日はまだ来ないかな
subtitles.english: I wonder if you're not coming yet today;

subtitles.original: 初めての感情知ってしまった
subtitles.english: I've learned a new feeling for the first time.

subtitles.original: 窓に飾った笑顔なぞって
subtitles.english: Tracing the smile I decorated on the window,

subtitles.original: 一人で宇宙を旅して
subtitles.english: I travel through space alone.

subtitles.original: それだけでいいはずだったのに
subtitles.english: That should have been enough, but...

subtitles.original: 君の手を握ってしまったら
subtitles.english: Now that I've taken your hand,

subtitles.original: 孤独を知らないこの街には
subtitles.english: to this city that knows no loneliness...

subtitles.original: もう二度と帰って来ることはできない
subtitles.english: I can never return again,

subtitles.original: 色化粧
subtitles.english: with this make-up of colors.

subtitles.original: 君が手を差し伸べた光で 影が生まれる
subtitles.english: With the light you reached out with, a shadow is born.

subtitles.original: 歌って聞かせて
subtitles.english: Sing it to me, let me hear

subtitles.original: この話の続き
subtitles.english: the rest of this story,

subtitles.original: 連れて行って見たことない星まで
subtitles.english: take me to a star I've never seen before.

subtitles.original: 誰にも声も届かない
subtitles.english: Atop the tower where no one's voice reaches,

subtitles.original: 高くそびえ立った塔の上
subtitles.english: the tower that towers so high.

subtitles.original: 飛ばす風船葛
subtitles.english: I release the balloon vines;

subtitles.original: 僕は君に笑ってほしいんだ
subtitles.english: I want you to smile.

subtitles.original: 満たされない穴を...
subtitles.english: The holes that cannot be filled...
